WEBVTT

00:03:59.395 --> 00:04:02.569
But this time, the Chinese didn't buy it.

00:04:02.593 --> 00:04:05.088
Fool me once...

00:04:05.112 --> 00:04:09.657
(Laughter)

00:04:09.681 --> 00:04:11.959
The rest is history.

00:04:11.983 --> 00:04:13.555
In just 30 years, China went from

00:04:13.579 --> 00:04:16.151
one of the poorest agricultural
countries in the world

00:04:16.175 --> 00:04:18.074
to its second-largest economy.

00:04:18.098 --> 00:04:20.130
Six hundred fifty million people

00:04:20.154 --> 00:04:21.745
were lifted out of poverty.

00:04:21.769 --> 00:04:24.733
Eighty percent of the entire
world's poverty alleviation

00:04:24.757 --> 00:04:26.958
during that period happened in China.

00:04:26.982 --> 00:04:29.607
In other words, all the new
and old democracies

00:04:29.631 --> 00:04:32.675
put together amounted to a mere fraction